arch:property.oc:show_val: Substantially more bone than F. 117 floor units, and somewhat better preserved. Wide variety of sizes and taxa, although sheep-size predominates. Light buff color with a little dark staining. Three distal tibias (all lefts) stand out in otherwise fairly even element distribution. Last number = 98

arch:string.div: The unique identifier for each contextual unit, matching those used in the central Çatalhöyük excavation database and in publications. The excavation uses single-context recording.
